'''Ghana''' nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ghana doƒo kple [[Togo]], [[Côte d'Ivoire]] kpakple [[Burkina Faso]]. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 22,113,000 lɔƒo. Woɖo Ghana tso ''Gold Coast'' kpakple ''British Togoland'' sinɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Ghana dukɔa xɔ ablɔɖeɖe tso Inglisiawo gbɔ le ƒe 1957 me.
